ADDITIONAL TERMS AND CONDITIONS FOR EDUCATIONAL INSTITUTIONS

This software is designed specifically for educational institutions. While the
MIT License above grants broad permissions, we encourage the following:

1. ATTRIBUTION

   - Please maintain credits to the original SAMS project
   - Include a notice that your system is "Powered by SAMS"

2. CONTRIBUTIONS

   - Contributions back to the main project are highly encouraged
   - Bug fixes, feature improvements, and documentation enhancements welcome

3. COMMERCIAL USE

   - Commercial use is permitted under the MIT License
   - For enterprise support contracts, please contact the project maintainers

4. DATA PRIVACY

   - Institutions using this software must comply with applicable data
     protection laws (GDPR, FERPA, COPPA, etc.)
   - Student data must be handled in accordance with local regulations
   - Implement appropriate security measures for sensitive information

5. LMS INTEGRATION

   - LTI 1.3 integration features comply with IMS Global standards
   - Ensure LMS platform licenses permit third-party tool integration
   - Maintain secure key management practices

6. THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS
   This software includes components licensed under their respective licenses:

   - PHPMailer: LGPL 2.1
   - Font Awesome: SIL OFL 1.1 (fonts), MIT (CSS)
   - Chart.js: MIT License
   - QRCode.js: MIT License
   - jQuery (if used): MIT License
   - Bootstrap (if used): MIT License

