DISCLAIMER

This software is provided for educational purposes. While every effort has been
made to ensure accuracy and security, the authors and contributors:

- Make no warranty regarding the software's fitness for any particular purpose
- Are not liable for any data loss or security breaches
- Recommend regular backups and security audits
- Suggest professional security review before production deployment

SECURITY NOTICE

Educational institutions must:

- Keep the software updated with security patches
- Use strong, unique passwords for all accounts
- Enable HTTPS/SSL for all deployments
- Regularly audit system logs and access patterns
- Comply with institutional IT security policies
- Implement appropriate firewalls and network security

SUPPORT AND UPDATES

- Community support: GitHub Issues and Discussions
- Security issues: Report privately to security@sams-project.org
- Documentation: /docs directory and online wiki
- Updates: Follow release notes and migration guides

================================================================================

VERSION HISTORY

v2.1.0 (November 24, 2025)

- Added LTI 1.3 LMS integration
- Implemented OpenID Connect SSO
- Added grade passback (AGS)
- Implemented deep linking
- Enhanced documentation

v2.0.0 (November 2025)

- Major UI overhaul with Cyberpunk theme
- Biometric integration support
- Real-time messaging system
- AI-powered analytics
- PWA implementation

v1.0.0 (October 2025)

- Initial release
- Basic attendance tracking
- Multi-role system
- Email notifications

